Critical Incident Support is available for employees who have been exposed to a serious incident in the workplace. All support is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
CONTINUE Health on Track Health on Track is your 3 phased workplace health program designed to support and improve your health and wellbeing. Body Moving – reaching your exercise goals and staying fit. Eating Well – supporting healthy choices and improving nutrition. Mind Matters – thinking positive and managing fatigue, stress and mental wellbeing.
CONTINUE Health Programs Health Services implements programs enabling our employees to improve or maintain their health and wellbeing, and to meet regulatory health requirements.
